OL,8,GKubrick's masterpiece was a must-have
OL,9,Gfor a space-themed EMF. '2001: A Space
OL,10,GOdyssey' stands as a visually stunning
OL,11,Gmasterpiece that creates overwhelming
OL,12,Gcosmic wonder through breathtaking
OL,13,Gcinematography and ambitious scope
OL,14,Gspanning human evolution. The
OL,15,Gthought-provoking narrative invites
OL,16,Gpersonal interpretation about
OL,17,Gconsciousness and humanity's place in
OL,18,Gthe universe. It's got HAL in it too.
